OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,FA gang responsible for importing #1
OL,7,Fmillion-worth of drugs told police
OL,8,Fmoney transfers between themselves and
OL,9,Fa man 4,600 miles away were for
OL,10,F"purchasing goats".
OL,12,FThe group of six, who were part of a
OL,13,Fmajor conspiracy to deal cocaine,
OL,14,Fcannabis and MDMA, came to light after
OL,15,Fofficers seized eight kilos of cocaine
OL,16,Ffrom a flight from Jamaica addressed
OL,17,Fto homes across Greater Manchester in
OL,18,FMarch 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
