FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,FArrests were made in connection with
OL,7,Fthe importation a year later, before
OL,8,Ffurther properties were searched in
OL,9,FGorton, Didsbury and Stockport, Bolton
OL,10,FCrown Court was told.
OL,12,FAt the Gorton property officers seized
OL,13,Ffour kilos of cocaine, thousands of
OL,14,FMDMA and 2CB tablets, a kilo of
OL,15,Fcannabis and #100,000 in cash.
OL,17,FThe total street value of the drugs
OL,18,Fseized as part of the investigation
OL,19,Fwas more than #1 million, Greater
OL,20,FManchester Police said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
