OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,FThe court heard several of the
OL,7,Fdefendants, aged 29-47, had contacted
OL,8,Fa man in Jamaica who was previously
OL,9,Fdeported from the UK.
OL,11,FTheir bank records showed money sent
OL,12,Fto the man which, when questioned, two
OL,13,Fof the defendants claimed were for the
OL,14,Fpurchasing of goats, not drugs, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard.
OL,17,FAfter being found guilty following a
OL,18,Ftrial the group were jailed for more
OL,19,Fthan 60 years in total.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,FDarren Bailey, Nathan Charles, Adrian
OL,7,FStephenson, Panashe Nyamariwata,
OL,8,FCharlene Bellamy and Kamica Morris
OL,9,Fwere handed sentences ranging from
OL,10,Ffour years to 19 years for conspiracy
OL,11,Fto import drugs.
OL,13,FHannah Conlon, 34, was found guilty of
OL,14,Fconspiracy to import class B drugs
OL,15,Fduring the same trial after over three
OL,16,Fkilos of cannabis was seized from
OL,17,FAmerica to be delivered to her home
OL,18,Faddress. She will be sentenced at
OL,19,FLiverpool Crown Court on Monday 20
OL,20,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
