OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,FDetective Constable Ryan O'Hanlon
OL,7,Fsaid: "This investigation has taken
OL,8,Fdrugs off the street worth over a
OL,9,Fmillion pounds.
OL,11,F"Drugs ruin lives and the crimes that
OL,12,Fare committed to fund habits that
OL,13,Fdealer's profit from, blight our
OL,14,Fcommunities.
OL,16,F"It shows the lengths that this group
OL,17,Fwent to for their own greed; bringing
OL,18,Fdrugs into the UK from abroad to
OL,19,Fmaximise their profits with no thought
OL,20,Ffor the misery that their actions
OL,21,Fcause.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1775855465
OL,3,C'For goats not drugs': Gang jailed for
OL,4,Cconspiracy to import #1m worth drugs
OL,6,F"Officers have worked tirelessly for
OL,7,Fover two years to ensure that these
OL,8,Foffenders were brought to justice `
OL,9,Fexecuting several warrants and
OL,10,Fgathering countless pieces of evidence
OL,11,Fwhich led to the jury seeing through
OL,12,Ftheir lies and finding all guilty.
OL,14,F"These sentences reflect the serious
OL,15,Fnature of the crimes they committed,
OL,16,Fand I am thankful they are now behind
OL,17,Fbars, and away from the communities
OL,18,Fthat officers work tirelessly to
OL,19,Fprotect."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
